data.description: Ideally located in like new condition sits this 4 BEDROOM plus BONUS room home--Just minutes to JBLM, shopping, dining and all services you would need.  Great room concept w/ island kitchen, quartz counters, and walk in pantry opens to family room  w/ gas fireplace and dining room.  Main floor flex room perfect for office or play area.  Upstairs 4 bedroom w/ convenient UPSTAIRS LAUNDRY.  Primary suite w/ attached 5 piece bath, walk in closet and views of Mt. Rainier.  Covered rear porch area, large and flat fenced yard gives room for everyone, attached 2 car garage; and NO HOA dues; AIR CONDITIONING and TANKLESS hot water.  Terrific location, NEWR, UPGRADES and SIZE makes this the smarter choice in the market.  VA Financing welcome.
